trans-unit.source: Represents the launch information required by a <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication"></xref> that has initiated in response to a peer collaboration invitation.
trans-unit.target: Representerer Start informasjonen som kreves av en <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication"> </xref> som har startet som svar på en node samarbeid invitasjonen.

trans-unit.source: An application can inspect the <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplicationLaunchInfo.Data%2A> and <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplicationLaunchInfo.Message%2A> properties in this class to get the information specific to the invitation that initiated the application launch.
trans-unit.target: Et program som kan undersøkes av <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplicationLaunchInfo.Data%2A>og <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplicationLaunchInfo.Message%2A>egenskapene i denne klassen for å få informasjon som er spesifikk for invitasjonen som startet programmet starter.</xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplicationLaunchInfo.Message%2A> </xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplicationLaunchInfo.Data%2A>

trans-unit.source: Access to this class requires a <xref:System.Security.Permissions.PermissionState> of <xref:System.Security.Permissions.PermissionState>.
trans-unit.target: Tilgang til denne klassen krever en <xref:System.Security.Permissions.PermissionState>av <xref:System.Security.Permissions.PermissionState>.</xref:System.Security.Permissions.PermissionState> </xref:System.Security.Permissions.PermissionState>

trans-unit.source: This state is created when the <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.Peer> collaboration session begins.
trans-unit.target: Denne tilstanden opprettes når den <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.Peer>samarbeidsøkten starter.</xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.Peer>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets application-defined binary data associated with the <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication"></xref> invitation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir Programdefinert binære data som er tilknyttet den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication"> </xref> invitasjonen.

trans-unit.source: This data blob is free form and is provided by the caller.
trans-unit.target: Denne data-blob er fritt format, og er angitt av oppkalleren.

trans-unit.source: The maximum amount of data that can be provided is 4,096 bytes.
trans-unit.target: Maksimal mengde data som kan angis er 4 096 byte.

trans-unit.source: The Data cannot be `null`.
trans-unit.target: Datatypen kan ikke være `null`.

trans-unit.source: An array of bytes that containing the data associated with the <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerCollaboration"></xref> invitation.
trans-unit.target: En bytematrise som inneholder dataene som er tilknyttet den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerCollaboration"> </xref> invitasjonen.

trans-unit.source: Get or set a message associated with the response to the <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerCollaboration"></xref> invitation.
trans-unit.target: Hente eller angi en melding som er knyttet til svaret på den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerCollaboration"> </xref> invitasjonen.

trans-unit.source: The maximum length for the message is 255 Unicode characters.
trans-unit.target: Den maksimale lengden for meldingen er 255 Unicode-tegn.

trans-unit.source: Unless explicitly specified, the default value for all properties is `null` for reference types.
trans-unit.target: Med mindre du eksplisitt angitt, er standardverdien for alle egenskaper `null` for referansetyper.

trans-unit.source: A text message associated with the <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerInvitationResponse"></xref> to the <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerCollaboration"></xref> invitation.
trans-unit.target: En tekstmelding som er tilknyttet den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerInvitationResponse"> </xref> til den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerCollaboration"> </xref> invitasjonen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication"></xref> for which the invitation was sent.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication"> </xref> for invitasjonen ble sendt.

trans-unit.source: Unless explicitly specified, the default value for all properties is `null` for reference types.
trans-unit.target: Med mindre du eksplisitt angitt, er standardverdien for alle egenskaper `null` for referansetyper.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication"></xref> for which the <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerCollaboration"></xref> invitation was sent.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication"> </xref> som den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerCollaboration"> </xref> invitasjonen ble sendt.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact"></xref> that sent the invitation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact"> </xref> som sendte invitasjonen.

trans-unit.source: Unless explicitly specified, the default value for all properties is `null` for reference types.
trans-unit.target: Med mindre du eksplisitt angitt, er standardverdien for alle egenskaper `null` for referansetyper.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact"></xref> that sent the invitation.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact"> </xref> som sendte invitasjonen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerEndPoint"></xref> from which the <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication"></xref> invitation was sent.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerEndPoint"> </xref> som den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication"> </xref> invitasjonen ble sendt.

trans-unit.source: Unless explicitly specified, the default value for all properties is `null` for reference types.
trans-unit.target: Med mindre du eksplisitt angitt, er standardverdien for alle egenskaper `null` for referansetyper.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerEndPoint"></xref> from which the invitation was sent.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerEndPoint"> </xref> fra invitasjonen ble sendt.
